i&amp;author=C+Iacono&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;journal=J+Gastrointest+Surg&amp;pages=281-287&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs11605-012-2043-y&amp;pmid=23065500">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">15.</div><div id="r15" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Sica GT, Ji H, Ros PR. CT and MR imaging of hepatic metastases. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2000;174(3): 691–698.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/ajr.174.3.1740691">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10701611/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=CT+and+MR+imaging+of+hepatic+metastases&amp;author=GT+Sica&amp;author=H+Ji&amp;author=PR+Ros&amp;publication_year=2000&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=691-698&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.174.3.1740691&amp;pmid=10701611">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">16.</div><div id="r16" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Soyer P, Poccard M, Boudiaf M, et al. Detection of hypovascular hepatic metastases at triple-phase helical CT: sensitivity of phases and comparison with surgical and histopathologic findings. <em>Radiology</em> 2004;231(2): 413–420.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/radiol.2312021639">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15044747/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Detection+of+hypovascular+hepatic+metastases+at+triple-phase+helical+CT%3A+sensitivity+of+phases+and+comparison+with+surgical+and+histopathologic+findings&amp;author=P+Soyer&amp;author=M+Poccard&amp;author=M+Boudiaf&a